text: Thomas Eyre may refer to: *Thomas Eyre (Jesuit) (1670–1715), English Jesuit *Thomas Eyre (divine) (1748–1810), Catholic theologian *Thomas Eyre (MP) (died 1628), MP for Salisbury * Thomas Eyre, President of Ushaw College, Dublin, 1794–1810 * Thomas Eyre (engineer) (died 1772), Irish military engineer and architect * Thomas Eyre (footballer) (fl. 1890s), football full back who played for Glasgow Ashfield, Lincoln City and Hamilton Academical ==See also== *
title: Thomas Eyre
